def multiply_complex_numbers(num1: str, num2: str) -> str:
    (a1, b1) = num1.split('+')
    (a2, b2) = num2.split('+')
    b1 = b1[:-1]
    b2 = b2[:-1]
    (a1, b1) = (int(a1), int(b1))
    (a2, b2) = (int(a2), int(b2))
    real_part = a1 * a2 + b1 * b2
    imag_part = b1 * a2 + a1 * b2
    return f'{real_part}+{imag_part}i'
